# --- Rust build output ---
target/
**/target/

# --- Cargo / lockfiles you probably don't want Aider to keep re-reading ---
Cargo.lock

# --- Editor / OS clutter ---
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~

# --- IDE settings ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.code-workspace

# --- Logs / temp / cache ---
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/*.cache
**/cache/
**/.cache/

# --- Generated / build artifacts ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/coverage/
**/reports/

# --- Documentation artifacts that are usually not source ---
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif
**/*.webp
**/*.pdf
**/*.svg

# --- Large data / binary assets ---
**/*.bin
**/*.exe
**/*.dll
**/*.so
**/*.dylib
**/*.a
**/*.o

# --- Node / web dependencies if any appear ---
node_modules/

# --- Python caches if tooling scripts appear ---
__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# --- Temporary helper files ---
tmp/
temp/
**/tmp/
**/temp/

# --- Keep the conventions file visible ---
!CONVENTIONS.md

# --- Ignore per-crate build noise if you have local tooling copies ---
**/artifacts/
**/generated/
**/gen/

# --- If you keep local scratch notes ---
notes/
scratch/
drafts/